<H3> <TI>   Prisons Director Denies Guards on Strike, Orders Probe </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA3001121594 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 1730 GMT 27 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA3001121594 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "National" newscast] </F>
  [Text] We just confirmed that guards at the Cali and 
Medellin prisons have joined the strike declared by La Picota 
Prison guards. In this regard, moments ago we interviewed 
Colonel Gustavo Socha Salamanca, general director of prisons. 
  [Begin recording] [Unidentified reporter] Col. Socha, what 
are the measures that the Penitentiary and Prison Institute is 
announcing in relation to the strike declared by guards at La 
Picota, La Modelo, and El Buen Pastor Prisons in Santa Fe de 
Bogota? 
