<H3> <TI>   Sen. Dupiton Said Linked to Izmery Assassination </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  FL0102180194 Port-au-Prince Radio Tropic FM in French 1430 
GMT 1 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL0102180194 </F>
<F P=104>  Port-au-Prince Radio Tropic FM </F>


