Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Monitored in progress] </F>
  [Text] ...December 1993 that the assassination of Antoine 
Izmery [Haitian businessman and Aristide supporter killed on 11 
September 1993] was allegedly worked out meticulously at the 
home of former Senate President Thomas Eddy Dupiton, an 
out-and-out [Aristide] adversary close to Colonel Joseph Michel 
