<H3> <TI>   Cuban-Japanese Sports Cooperation Discussed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  FL0202195494 Havana Radio Progreso Network in Spanish 1200 
GMT 2 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL0202195494 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Progreso Network </F>


