<F P=100> Brazil </F>
<H3> <TI>   Judge Rejects Injunction Against Constitutional Revision </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PY0302222794 Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network in Portuguese 
2100 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY0302222794 </F>
<F P=104>  Brasilia Voz do Brasil Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Portuguese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Supreme Court Justice Marco Aurelio Mello today 
rejected an injunction to suspend the constitutional revision in 
Congress. The injunction had been filed by the leaders of the PT 
[Workers Party], the PDT [Democratic Labor Party], the PC do B 
[Communist Party of Brazil], and the PSTU [expansion unknown]. 

</TEXT>

